---
title: Tex-Mex Beef & Pork Meatballs with Cauliflower Rice & Yoghurt
description: We’re checking off some must-haves with tonight’s dinner. A scrumptious serving of plump beef & pork meatballs, check. Cooked in our favourite Tex-Mex spice, check. What about a cauliflower rice, for a light and fluffy addition, check. A load of veggies including sticky caramelised onion, check again. This recipe passes with flying colours!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
